race.comment: CHESTIME (8) improved sharply second-up to score at Gunnedah in style and looks set to keep progressing. Draws kindly and can win again. BARCELONA EXPRESS (3) is going better than his form suggests and should be hitting his straps now fourth-up. Is already a track and trip winner and is drawn to get the gun run. Must be taken seriously. PUZZLE DESIGNER (1) is ready to strike third-up after two solid runs back. Gets a key booking in Bullock who will be putting his skills to the test from the wide draw. EJECT (2) bounced back to winning form when scoring by a nose over 1600m at Moree last start and rates a chance in this field.
